# Elastic Security (Elasticsearch Query Language) Queries

All queries designed for Elastic Stack with Beats (Filebeat, Auditbeat, Winlogbeat) data. Adjust index names and field mappings based on your Elastic configuration.

## T1566.001 - Spearphishing Attachment

Detects office applications spawning command interpreters.

```kusto
process.parent.name : ("winword.exe" OR "excel.exe" OR "powerpnt.exe") 
AND process.name : ("powershell.exe" OR "cmd.exe" OR "wscript.exe" OR "cscript.exe")
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
process.parent.name : ("winword.exe" OR "excel.exe" OR "powerpnt.exe") 
AND process.name : ("powershell.exe" OR "cmd.exe" OR "wscript.exe" OR "cscript.exe")
| stats count() as event_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen 
  by process.parent.name, process.name, host.name
```

## T1059.001 - Obfuscated PowerShell Execution

Identifies PowerShell processes with encoding and obfuscation indicators.

```kusto
process.name : "powershell.exe" 
AND (process.command_line : "-EncodedCommand" 
  OR process.command_line : "IEX (New-Object Net.WebClient" 
  OR process.command_line : "Invoke-Expression"
  OR process.command_line : "[Convert]::FromBase64String"
  OR process.command_line : "DownloadString")
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
process.name : "powershell.exe" 
AND (process.command_line : "-EncodedCommand" 
  OR process.command_line : "IEX (New-Object Net.WebClient" 
  OR process.command_line : "Invoke-Expression"
  OR process.command_line : "[Convert]::FromBase64String"
  OR process.command_line : "DownloadString")
| stats count() as event_count, values(user.name) as users, values(host.name) as devices
  by process.command_line, host.name, host.os.name
```

## T1003 - OS Credential Dumping

Detects credential dumping tool execution and specific commands.

```kusto
(process.parent.name : ("mimikatz.exe" OR "procdump.exe" OR "ntdsutil.exe")
OR process.command_line : ("sekurlsa::logonpasswords" OR "sekurlsa::ekeys" OR "-ma lsass" OR "lsadump::sam" OR "lsadump::secrets"))
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("Picus" OR "Qualys" OR "Rapid7" OR "Tenable"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
(process.parent.name : ("mimikatz.exe" OR "procdump.exe" OR "ntdsutil.exe")
OR process.command_line : ("sekurlsa::logonpasswords" OR "sekurlsa::ekeys" OR "-ma lsass" OR "lsadump::sam" OR "lsadump::secrets"))
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("Picus" OR "Qualys" OR "Rapid7" OR "Tenable"))
| stats count() as event_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen
  by process.parent.name, process.command_line, host.name, user.name
```

## T1574.002 - DLL Side-loading

Identifies suspicious DLL execution from non-standard paths.

```kusto
file.name : "*.dll" 
AND (file.path : "*\\Users\\Public\\*" 
  OR file.path : "*\\Temp\\*" 
  OR file.path : "*\\ProgramData\\*"
  OR file.path : "*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp*")
AND NOT (file.path : ("*Windows Update*" OR "*SoftwareDistribution*" OR "*Microsoft Defender*" OR "*Windows Defender*"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
file.name : "*.dll" 
AND (file.path : "*\\Users\\Public\\*" 
  OR file.path : "*\\Temp\\*" 
  OR file.path : "*\\ProgramData\\*"
  OR file.path : "*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp*")
AND NOT (file.path : ("*Windows Update*" OR "*SoftwareDistribution*" OR "*Microsoft Defender*" OR "*Windows Defender*"))
| stats count() as event_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen
  by file.name, file.path, host.name
```

## T1071.001 - Suspicious C2 Connections

Detects HTTPS connections to suspicious TLDs.

```kusto
destination.port : 443 
AND (destination.domain : "*.ru" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.ir" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.gq" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.tk" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.ml" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.ga")
AND NOT (destination.domain : ("*.yandex.ru" OR "*.vk.com" OR "*.rambler.ru" OR "*.mail.ru" OR "microsoft.com" OR "google.com" OR "cloudflare.com"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
destination.port : 443 
AND network.protocol : "https"
AND (destination.domain : "*.ru" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.ir" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.gq" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.tk" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.ml" 
  OR destination.domain : "*.ga")
AND NOT (destination.domain : ("*.yandex.ru" OR "*.vk.com" OR "*.rambler.ru" OR "*.mail.ru" OR "microsoft.com" OR "google.com" OR "cloudflare.com"))
| stats count() as connection_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen,
  values(process.name) as processes
  by destination.domain, destination.port, host.name
```

## T1547.001 - Registry-Based Persistence

Monitors Windows Run registry key modifications.

```kusto
registry.key : "*Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run*"
AND event.action : ("RegistryValueSet" OR "RegistryValueModified")
AND NOT (registry.key : ("*Microsoft Edge Update*" OR "*MicrosoftEdgeAutoLaunch*" OR "*RtkAudUService*" OR "*OneDrive*" OR "*Windows Update*"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
registry.key : "*Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Run*"
AND event.action : ("RegistryValueSet" OR "RegistryValueModified")
AND NOT (registry.key : ("*Microsoft Edge Update*" OR "*MicrosoftEdgeAutoLaunch*" OR "*RtkAudUService*" OR "*OneDrive*" OR "*Windows Update*"))
| stats count() as modification_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen,
  values(registry.value) as registry_values
  by registry.key, registry.path, host.name, process.name, user.name
```

## T1218 - LOLBin Abuse

Detects Living-off-the-Land Binaries with suspicious command-line parameters.

```kusto
process.name : ("regsvr32.exe" OR "mshta.exe" OR "rundll32.exe" OR "certutil.exe")
AND (process.command_line : ("http://" OR "https://" OR "hxxp://" OR "hxxps://") 
  OR process.command_line : "*.dll*" 
  OR process.command_line : ("javascript:" OR "vbscript:"))
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("spool" OR "Prnntfy.dll" OR "pla.dll" OR "printui.dll" OR "ntprint.dll" OR "Windows\\System32" OR "Program Files"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
process.name : ("regsvr32.exe" OR "mshta.exe" OR "rundll32.exe" OR "certutil.exe")
AND (process.command_line : ("http://" OR "https://" OR "hxxp://" OR "hxxps://") 
  OR process.command_line : "*.dll*" 
  OR process.command_line : ("javascript:" OR "vbscript:"))
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("spool" OR "Prnntfy.dll" OR "pla.dll" OR "printui.dll" OR "ntprint.dll" OR "Windows\\System32" OR "Program Files"))
| stats count() as command_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen
  by process.name, process.command_line, host.name, user.name
```

## T1027 - Obfuscation & Encoding

Identifies script execution with obfuscation indicators.

```kusto
process.name : ("powershell.exe" OR "cscript.exe" OR "wscript.exe" OR "mshta.exe" OR "regsvr32.exe" OR "rundll32.exe")
AND (process.command_line : "-EncodedCommand" 
  OR process.command_line : "frombase64string" 
  OR process.command_line : ("powershell -e " OR "powershell /e " OR "powershell -enc " OR "powershell /enc ")
  OR process.command_line : "mshta vbscript:" 
  OR process.command_line : "javascript:" 
  OR process.command_line : ("[convert]::frombase64" OR "System.Convert" OR "[System.Text.Encoding]"))
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("Nutanix" OR "VMware" OR "Hyper-V") OR user.name : ("SYSTEM" OR "NETWORK SERVICE"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
process.name : ("powershell.exe" OR "cscript.exe" OR "wscript.exe" OR "mshta.exe" OR "regsvr32.exe" OR "rundll32.exe")
AND (process.command_line : "-EncodedCommand" 
  OR process.command_line : "frombase64string" 
  OR process.command_line : ("powershell -e " OR "powershell /e " OR "powershell -enc " OR "powershell /enc ")
  OR process.command_line : "mshta vbscript:" 
  OR process.command_line : "javascript:" 
  OR process.command_line : ("[convert]::frombase64" OR "System.Convert" OR "[System.Text.Encoding]"))
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("Nutanix" OR "VMware" OR "Hyper-V") OR user.name : ("SYSTEM" OR "NETWORK SERVICE"))
| stats count() as event_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen
  by process.name, process.command_line, host.name, user.name
```

## T1567.002 - Data Exfiltration Over Web

Detects file transfer utilities with web protocols.

```kusto
process.name : ("curl.exe" OR "wget.exe" OR "ftp.exe")
AND (process.command_line : ("http://" OR "https://" OR "ftp://" OR "ftps://"))
AND NOT (user.name : "SYSTEM" AND process.executable : "C:\\Windows\\System32\\*")
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("Windows Update" OR "Microsoft Update" OR "NuGet"))
```

### Full Query with Context

```kusto
index: logs-endpoint.events-* 
process.name : ("curl.exe" OR "wget.exe" OR "ftp.exe")
AND (process.command_line : ("http://" OR "https://" OR "ftp://" OR "ftps://"))
AND NOT (user.name : "SYSTEM" AND process.executable : "C:\\Windows\\System32\\*")
AND NOT (process.command_line : ("Windows Update" OR "Microsoft Update" OR "NuGet"))
| stats count() as command_count, min(timestamp) as first_seen, max(timestamp) as last_seen
  by process.name, process.command_line, host.name, user.name
```

